    "causal_summary": "Phase 005 of packet 035 (unified command-contract architecture). Retrofit the remaining commands, the 3 sibling improvement lanes, and non-deep-loop surfaces to the phase-003 compiled contract; land the Gate-2 sub-threshold routing offer; land pacing/resume (design-first: resumable sub-invocations, cache, budget policy); land the council convergence rule (F-018); and flip the per-command feature flags on per the promotion rule. Closes F-018/023/024/026/032/033/034. Absorbs plan-review gaps GAP-11/33/41/44/54.",
